I mean, I'm sorry you're having
to go through all this.

17:29.680 --> 17:32.400
Um, speak to psych about
the patient,

17:32.400 --> 17:34.040
but I wouldn't hold my breath.

17:34.040 --> 17:35.520
I know it's hard... PAGER BEEPS

17:35.520 --> 17:37.280
