18:10.280 --> 18:13.000
And because that was your
third attempt,

18:13.000 --> 18:16.760
that means, unfortunately,
according to...

18:16.760 --> 18:19.440
We can still have another go, right?

18:19.440 --> 18:23.480
I'm... I'm very sorry to say that,
as per our guidelines,

18:23.480 --> 18:26.360
three rounds
is all you're eligible for.

18:26.360 --> 18:28.120
It can't be.

18:28.120 --> 18:29.480
I'm really sorry.

18:30.520 --> 18:33.040
Um, some...some people
try again privately,

18:33.040 --> 18:34.600
if they can find the money.

18:35.800 --> 18:38.600
MS HOUGHTON:  Roll up!
Roll up! Who's up next, then?

18:42.880 --> 18:44.360
Or you could just not bother.

18:47.240 --> 18:48.960
I'm sorry?

18:48.960 --> 18:50.240
