18:50.240 --> 18:52.680
with the number of eggs
that we've managed

18:52.680 --> 18:54.040
to harvest on your last cycles,

18:54.040 --> 18:56.800
plus the level of the AMH hormones
that you've got,

18:56.800 --> 18:59.320
you've got about a 1% chance
of success.

19:02.320 --> 19:05.480
1%?  Absolute maximum.

19:05.480 --> 19:08.880
Why's no-one told us this before?

19:08.880 --> 19:10.400
I'm telling you now.

19:14.080 --> 19:17.360
Look, why don't you go home,
regroup, think about things

19:17.360 --> 19:19.160
like egg donation, adoption?

19:19.160 --> 19:21.640
But, honestly, you're not
having a baby with IVF.

19:24.600 --> 19:27.880
Thanks, Doctor.
I appreciate your honesty.

