'Mum says hi.'
Hi...

20:02.600 --> 20:03.680
..Pauline.

20:03.680 --> 20:05.200
He says hi back.

20:05.200 --> 20:07.080
Er, the place is looking great.

20:07.080 --> 20:09.120
You'd never know there was
a wake here three hours ago.

20:09.120 --> 20:10.440
HARRY LAUGHS Christ.

20:10.440 --> 20:12.920
'Ah, don't worry,
