21:20.440 --> 21:22.360
Well, no, it doesn't.

21:22.360 --> 21:26.040
It looks nothing like it's meant to.

21:26.040 --> 21:30.000
Who told you what it's meant
to look like?

21:30.000 --> 21:32.080
Well, you just see it on, like...

21:34.360 --> 21:35.400
..I dunno.

21:36.720 --> 21:39.520
Don't want to make
any assumptions but...

21:40.480 --> 21:43.760
..but I've probably seen a lot
more vulvas than you have.

21:43.760 --> 21:45.280
At work, I hope.

21:50.560 --> 21:52.080
Have you, um...

21:53.880 --> 21:56.920
..talked to anyone about this?

21:56.920 --> 22:00.080
Yeah, I actually texted
everyone a picture.

22:00.080 --> 22:01.640
Oh, cool, same here.

22:06.120 --> 22:09.000
How would you feel if I, um...

22:09.000 --> 22:10.480
..brought a colleague over

22:10.480 --> 22:12.960
who knows much more
about this stuff than I do?

22:14.960 --> 22:16.600
Just for a quick chat?

22:18.400 --> 22:19.720
Might be helpful.

22:21.840 --> 22:22.960
OK.

22:29.600 --> 22:30.880
I'll be ten minutes.

22:41.960 --> 22:43.720
PAGER BEEPS

22:43.720 --> 22:45.360
I'm just here!

22:45.360 --> 22:47.840
Who's bleeping me?
Time to turn on the charm.

22:51.400 --> 22:52.560
Sorry to bother you.

22:52.560 --> 22:54.760
Are you on call
for psychiatry today?

22:54.760 --> 22:56.880
No, I just stole their bleep.

22:56.880 --> 22:59.680
HE LAUGHS Adam Kay, obs and gynae.

22:59.680 --> 23:02.480
You just introducing yourself
to every department?

23:02.480 --> 23:05.240
This is the person who stops
people killing themselves?

23:05.240 --> 23:08.400
Um, could you possibly review
a patient for me?

23:08.400 --> 23:11.760
19 years old, just performed some
cosmetic surgery on her vulva.

23:11.760 --> 23:14.240
