jump off a bridge this morning,

23:14.240 --> 23:17.320
a student in frank psychosis,
what's this one?

23:17.320 --> 23:18.960
Another suicide attempt.

23:18.960 --> 23:20.600
Please, even if it's just a minute.

23:20.600 --> 23:22.440
There's only one of me,
I just can't.

23:22.440 --> 23:24.600
Well, what am I meant to tell her?
Tell her to see her GP

23:24.600 --> 23:26.880
for referral to community
mental health.

23:26.880 --> 23:28.400
It's just not an emergency.

23:28.400 --> 23:31.040
Since when did we only fucking see
life and death emergencies

23:31.040 --> 23:32.320
in this place?

23:32.320 --> 23:35.400
You losing your shit at me isn't
going to magic up any more doctors.

23:35.400 --> 23:36.920
Sorry, sorry.

23:36.920 --> 23:39.280
I've had a real day of it.

23:39.280 --> 23:41.960
I will see her
when I get two seconds.

23:41.960 --> 23:44.600
Thank you. I owe you.

23:54.760 --> 23:56.000
KNOCK ON DOOR

