That's really kind.

31:14.520 --> 31:16.320
So kind.

31:17.560 --> 31:19.080
Properly kind.

31:19.080 --> 31:21.960
Don't feel like you have to.
I don't feel like I have to.

31:21.960 --> 31:24.040
Obviously, I would, but... PARTY MUSIC

31:24.040 --> 31:27.240
This feels very much like a no.
No, I just...

31:27.240 --> 31:29.280
I wasn't gonna do this today,
clearly.

31:29.280 --> 31:31.320
What, you shat yourself
in the IMAX again?

31:31.320 --> 31:32.960
No, I've...I've been thinking.

31:34.280 --> 31:36.560
I'm going to have
to relieve you of best man duties.

31:39.240 --> 31:44.240
Right, you're demoting me
to just man?

31:44.240 --> 31:46.000
Not just man.

31:46.000 --> 31:47.440
You're a man who I love.

31:49.800 --> 31:52.480
But I need the day to run smoothly,
and I know what your job's like.

31:53.680 --> 31:55.000
I always get there in the end.

31:55.000 --> 31:56.440
You always get there at the end.

31:56.440 --> 31:58.720
Look, and if there's some
big emergency,

31:58.720 --> 32:00.720
are you honestly telling me
you'd leave it behind?

32:04.160 --> 32:05.280
Course you wouldn't.

32:17.440 --> 32:19.600
There you are.

32:19.600 --> 32:23.120
Hey.  Adam tells me you organised
this all by yourself.

32:23.120 --> 32:25.440
Extraordinary.  Ah.

32:25.440 --> 32:28.720
Thank you. Adam was too busy
saving babies.

32:28.720 --> 32:31.840
Expect you'll get used
to doing things on your own.

32:31.840 --> 32:33.280
I will?

32:33.280 --> 32:34.600
You'll have to.

32:34.600 --> 32:36.560
You'll think it's just
a junior doctor thing,

32:36.560 --> 32:38.840
but it gets worse and worse,
believe me.

32:38.840 --> 32:43.120
Still, marriage is all about taking
someone on as they are, isn't it?

32:43.120 --> 32:45.200
Which of us is perfect?

32:46.760 --> 32:50.360
I, for example, have eczema.

32:50.360 --> 32:52.200
He's perfect for me.

32:54.000 --> 32:56.280
That's all that matters,
really, isn't it?

33:08.000 --> 33:09.240
Look who it is.

33:12.720 --> 33:14.440
You all right?  Yeah.

33:14.440 --> 33:16.080
I'm fine.  You sure?

33:18.200 --> 33:19.840
No, I'm not.

33:19.840 --> 33:22.200
Greg's just dumped me
as his best man,

33:22.200 --> 33:24.480
and there's been a complaint
about me, a bad one,

33:24.480 --> 33:27.680
to the GMC, and a baby's very ill,

33:27.680 --> 33:29.040
and I lied in the notes

33:29.040 --> 33:31.120
and I really don't know
what's gonna happen.

33:31.120 --> 33:32.600
What the fuck, Adam?

33:32.600 --> 33:35.680
It'll be fine.
They're getting me a lawyer.

33:35.680 --> 33:36.960
How could you let that happen?

33:36.960 --> 33:38.800
I thought you were good at your job.

33:38.800 --> 33:40.880
That's exactly why I didn't tell
you.

33:40.880 --> 33:43.200
You're just an embarrassment,
aren't you?  Shut up!

33:43.200 --> 33:45.760
Adam?  Sorry, I was miles away.

33:45.760 --> 33:48.920
Erm, yep, I'm...I'm fine, thanks.

33:50.560 --> 33:53.000
Relax.  Mm-hm.  It's gonna be fun.

33:53.000 --> 33:55.240
It is fun.
Everyone's having a nice time.

33:55.240 --> 33:56.640
Everyone?  Yep.

33:56.640 --> 33:58.840
Your mum's had a glass of wine.

33:58.840 --> 34:00.920
We found her one made
of actual glass.

34:00.920 --> 34:02.400
Oh, fancy.

34:02.400 --> 34:05.000
Then she did a quick DJ set,
mostly ambient house,

34:05.000 --> 34:07.200
but she chucked in a bit
of hard NRG.

34:07.200 --> 34:10.000
BOTH LAUGH
OK, it was more ghetto house.

