34:16.280 --> 34:17.520
Like a beard trimmer.

34:19.880 --> 34:21.520
Oh, I was just talking to Pawel,
what an angel.

34:21.520 --> 34:24.640
Pawel?  Yeah, one of your work
friends, a porter, I think?

34:24.640 --> 34:28.920
Yes, sorry, er, we tend to use
nicknames at work.

34:28.920 --> 34:30.880
Oh, yeah, what is it, then?

34:30.880 --> 34:33.640
Pav? Pav... Pavpav.

34:33.640 --> 34:35.520
Wow, creative.

34:35.520 --> 34:37.200
Right, come say hi to Mum.

34:37.200 --> 34:39.120
She's already started a conga line.

34:39.120 --> 34:41.200
I'm gonna just get a quick drink.

34:41.200 --> 34:43.160
Yeah.  I'll be...

34:43.160 --> 34:46.120
Hello!  Hey! LAUGHTER

34:46.120 --> 34:48.480
Thanks so much for coming, guys.

34:48.480 --> 34:51.120
It's all right. It's the first
night out we've had in years.

